# 3 DRG Personnel Killed In Encounter With Naxalites In Sukma District

Author: Alan Warsaw

Publish Time: 2023-02-25T05:11:59+00:00

Update Time: 2023-02-26T17:12:47+00:00

Images: ['[bloomberg_1474022425_1474022432-800x445.jpg](https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/bloomberg_1474022425_1474022432-800x445.jpg)']

